{"type": "article", "id": 16686, "title": "Pipe 沙发", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-28T06:14:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110621wITLbVueck2RXGCr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是德国设计师 Sebastian Herkner 为意大利家具品牌 Moroso 设计的沙发，为了与市场流行的细长结构不同，他使用了直径 8 厘米粗的金属管结构。座椅和靠背也并不显轻巧，用了柔软的纺织品与之对比，可以替换不同的面料。沙发还另配一张桌子，也是使用了较粗的管子，以此表现设计师的自我风格。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143957EoD4qNxSK1XCvWJ9.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143958CjaKuUocBEIyGqhm.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143959IuxD43cwtfdoZapY.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261439598ZSFlCPsb14pJB3G.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"484\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.51709402\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}